query:
SELECT p.id, p.eventId, p.name, p.email, p.phone, e.title as eventTitle
FROM participants p
JOIN events e ON p.eventId = e.id
WHERE p.name = 'Lynnette Glory' OR p.email = 'lynnette.glory@gmail.com'
ORDER BY p.eventId, p.id;
